| `nginx` | nginx:stable-alpine | `APP_PORT` (8000) | Sirve la app, proxea PHP a `php:9000` |
| `php` | docker/php/Dockerfile | interno 9000 | php-fpm, healthcheck `php -v` |
| `queue` | docker/queue/Dockerfile | — | `php artisan queue:work` |
| `scheduler` | docker/scheduler/Dockerfile | — | loop `php artisan schedule:run` |
