| `minio` | minio/minio | `MINIO_CONSOLE_PORT` (9001) | healthcheck curl /minio/health/live |
| `minio-setup` | minio/mc | — | Init container, crea el bucket, exit 0 |
| `mailpit` | axllent/mailpit | `MAILPIT_UI_PORT` (8025) / `MAILPIT_SMTP_PORT` (1025) | |
